Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Management
Sumitomo Mitsui Trust Asset Management Company, Ltd. operates as an international financial services firm and offers investment advisory services. The Company manages portfolios of Japanese and global bonds and equities, Chinese and other Asian equities, alternative products, and REITs for public pension funds, mutual aid pension funds, and corporate pension funds.




